Dear Mrs Marash

I refer to your meeting with Mrs Maya Fankhauser on December 5th, 2018

Please find enclosed the proposal letter for the changing of the mandate as=
 well as the contract "Confirmation of Investment Management Mandate Vontob=
el Specials" and some fact sheets.

May I kindly ask you to duly sign the letter and the contract and return us=
 both originals by mail or courier.

I thank you in advance for your kind cooperation.

With best regards


Manuela Mettler
Assistant





